Henry Street, north side, east from Scammel (left of No.1) to Grand (right of No. 2) Street's, showing this frontage in two portions. The demolition appearing in the second item is detailed in third view. These bear No's. 317 (demolished), 319 (standing vacant) and 321 (new brick garage). All of these were formerly of frame construction, those at the left having a brick front. Their rears abuted onto the rears of buildings that face on Grand Street.
